General.Name: Rejlers AB (publ)
General.Description: Rejlers AB (publ) provides technical and engineering consultancy services in Sweden, Finland, Norway, and the United Arab Emirates. It serves energy, industry, construction, property, and infrastructure sectors. The company was formerly known as Rejlerkoncernen AB and changed its name to Rejlers AB (publ) in July 2013. Rejlers AB (publ) was founded in 1942 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.
